key_0.name: Grateful Dead
key_0.set1: It's A Man's World (take 1) It's A Man's World (take 2) It's A Man's World (take 3) Bob! Bob!...Bob Do It > Jerry slipknotian noodles Slipknot > Franklin's Tower messing around > Blues jam(schoolgirl?)
key_0.comment:
*this is the date and location given.
Strange listen.
Worth it for the Franklin's Tower which Jerry refuses to let die, otherwise its pretty painful.
There was a decent amount of hiss which given the rehearsal nature of the recording is distraction. XNoise did an adequate job at minimal settings.
Thanks to M.Townshend for sharing his cassette source.
